items.name: Classic Beef Burger
items.description: Made with imported Australian Angus beef, paired with fresh lettuce, tomatoes, and secret sauce. Juicy in every bite.

reviews.comment: The patty is really thick and very juicy!
A little salty, but good overall.

items.name: Italian Tomato Spaghetti
items.description: Traditional Sicilian flavor. Sweet and sour tomato meat sauce coats every strand of pasta, topped with Parmesan cheese.

reviews.comment: The noodles are chewy, and there's plenty of sauce.
